fields.name: Palabras Clave
fields.definition: Keywords to express the subject of the image. Keywords may be free text and don’t have to be taken from a controlled vocabulary. Codes from the controlled vocabulary IPTC Subject NewsCodes must go to the "Subject Code" field.
fields.help_text: Terminos o frases usadas para indicar lo que sucede en la imagen.

fields.name: Evento
fields.definition: Names or describes the specific event at which the photo was taken.

fields.name: Género
fields.definition: Artistic, style, journalistic, product or other genre(s) of the image (expressed by a term from any Controlled Vocabulary)
fields.help_text: Arte, periodismo, realismo u otro género.

fields.name: Lugar
fields.definition: A location shown in the image.

fields.name: Organización
fields.definition: Name of the organisation or company which is featured in the image.
fields.help_text: Nombre de la organización en la imagen.

fields.name: Persona
fields.definition: Name of a person shown in the image.
fields.help_text: Nombre de la persona en la fotografía.

fields.name: Fecha
fields.definition: Designates the date and optionally the time the content of the image was created rather than the date of the creation of the digital representation.
fields.help_text: La fecha en que fue tomada la imagen, o el periodo.
